        <abstract>
            <p>Still working on book and has completed 620 out of 700 pages.</p> 
<p>Rewrote memoir [on mimicry in Amazon Lepidoptera] for <hi rend="italic">Trans. Linn. Soc. Lond.</hi> [23 (1862): 495–566].</p>  
<p>Edwin Brown, HWB’s earliest naturalist friend, will have a hard time classifying <hi rend="italic">Carabi</hi> as he is unable to travel.</p> 
        </abstract>
